Titolo: Tangle Tower

Anno: 2019

Descrizione: Tangle Tower (also known as Detective Grimoire: Tangle Tower) is a murder mystery point-and-click adventure game developed and published by SFB Games. It is a sequel to the 2014 game Detective Grimoire and the third entry in the Detective Grimoire series. The game was launched with the Apple Arcade service on September 19, 2019 and was later released for Nintendo Switch and Steam on October 22, 2019, followed by PlayStation 4 and Xbox One on October 6, 2021.